Class Smarty

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Smarty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PersonType, Simpleton
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContractWorker, HourlyWorker

    public abstract class Smarty
extends java.lang.Object
implements PersonType, Simpleton
    Abstract class that implements the PersonType and Simpleton Interfaces and adds additional functionality for a person who can be described as smart. Smart people can do everything a simpleton can, but they also have an IQ and an income.
